			"description": "<ul><li><p>An invisible creature is impossible to see without the aid of magic or a special sense (it gains no benefits from this condition against creatures still able to see it).</p></li><li><p>An invisible creature is heavily obscured for the purpose of hiding.</p></li><li><p>An invisible creature's location can be detected by noises it makes or tracks it leaves.</p></li><li><p>Attack rolls against an invisible creature are made with disadvantage.</p></li><li><p>An invisible creature makes attack rolls with advantage.</p></li></ul>",
